{"tid":601572,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【胡椒/黑椒撚】有無巴絲好撚中意食咩都落胡椒黑椒","createTime":"2018-03-22T10:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T14:46:48.000Z","uid":162853,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69249b3f4f256eb9f6e2b9821b9225ec7a48489c","tid":601572,"uid":162853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n無論食中餐西餐都好  都要落一通黑椒  無黑椒就落胡椒粉<br />\n隻味真係好正 尤其係黑椒<br />\n嗰陣特有嘅香味同埋辣辣地嘅味道真係令人欲罷不能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我次次食野都要灑勁多  最好就鋪滿整個平面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但平時同屋企人/朋友食飯都會被佢地用奇怪嘅目光望住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有類似情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3548e37f42fa3f6637096438940b0ad271a01d7a","tid":601572,"uid":26971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"成日比人話重口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826d6e4a618d6fcde95170baf20a7f78a6ff764a","tid":601572,"uid":127269,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:28:03.000Z","msg":"食火腿通唔落胡椒粉不如唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa52cfccefd0bf410fced24e6b233976e8d5617","tid":601572,"uid":162853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3548e37f42fa3f6637096438940b0ad271a01d7a","tid":601572,"uid":26971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"成日比人話重口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但轉頭佢地自己又起勢咁落辣椒醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc3479e6f7a455a9ca8e85ef269d42044db017a","tid":601572,"uid":149566,"like":